      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-sts-pmt-key
                                               w-cnt-sts-pmt-tes
                                               w-cnt-sts-pmt-cor
                                               w-cnt-sts-pmt-rig
                                               w-cnt-sts-pmt-pie      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
