           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      34                   to   v-car                  .
           move      04                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      47                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-tes-des-cau (1)    to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
           go to     pmt-key-reg-800.
