      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-det-num-dfd-flg      .
       det-num-dfd-050.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test preliminari                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
