      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-mgr-num-prt       =    w-tes-num-prt
                     go to det-num-dfd-200.
       det-num-dfd-500.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test su tipo movimento Iva                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-mgr-tip-iva       not  = "5"
                     go to det-num-dfd-200.
       det-num-dfd-600.
